OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers in
OL,6,Fthe north gradually fade as winds ease
OL,7,Fovernight. Elsewhere, skies clear,
OL,8,Fespecially in the south, with some
OL,9,Fpatchy fog possible later across the
OL,10,Ffar southwest by dawn.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FMostly dry with sunny spells
OL,13,Fon Sunday. Light winds for most, but
OL,14,Fbreezy along North Sea coasts. The odd
OL,15,Fshower possible in the north later.
OL,16,FFeeling warm in any sunshine.
